we have students who
are copying and pasting

00:29:29.347 --> 00:29:31.065
their badges they get on Khan Academy

00:29:31.065 --> 00:29:35.604
and bootstrapping the iteration
forth, they're so proud of it.

00:29:35.604 --> 00:29:38.396
Something like that
and the volunteer badge

00:29:38.396 --> 00:29:41.945
could be a pretty
powerful mark of whatever.

00:29:41.945 --> 00:29:43.546
Jeff: Yeah, so call to
action, for anyone interested

00:29:43.546 --> 00:29:44.967
in the next -

00:29:44.967 --> 00:29:45.896
Sal: And also developing modules.

