especially these marquee employers,

00:59:02.528 --> 00:59:03.795
then maybe even the Khan Academy,

00:59:03.795 --> 00:59:07.195
because we have a brand and
it's in the right place,

00:59:08.033 --> 00:59:11.144
you don't face that difficulty
of starting a university

00:59:11.144 --> 00:59:12.285
that no one's ever heard of.

00:59:12.285 --> 00:59:14.728
People will hear of this
university on day one.

00:59:14.728 --> 00:59:17.689
I think something like
that, if that's successful,

00:59:17.689 --> 00:59:21.145
then all of a sudden the tuition
inflation becomes very hard to justify.

